{"type":"message","id":"1631d2b7","parentId":"f7f37c99","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:30:30.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hmndgmf6qtj1_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这张图片展示了一个名为 `openclaw.json` 的 JSON 配置文件。该文件看起来是一个人工智能、自动化工具或开发者平台的配置，其中包含模型定义、工作区路径、工具配置文件和安全设置。\n\n以下是图片中可见内容的详细分类：\n\n### 1. 模型定义 (第 285-295 行)\n这部分为特定的人工智能模型定义了别名（Aliases），使用的是 \"minimaxmax\" 提供商的模型：\n*   **minimax-m2.5-lightning**: 别名为 `\"minimax-m2.5-lightning\"`。\n*   **minimax-m2.5-highspeed**: 别名为 `\"minimax-m2.5-highspeed\"`。\n*   **minimax-m2.7**: 别名为 `\"minimax-m2.7\"`。\n*   **minimax-m2.7-highspeed**: 别名为 `\"minimax-m2.7-highspeed\"`。\n\n### 2. 工作区与列表配置 (第 297-306 行)\n*   **workspace**: 设置为路径 `\"/Users/diehe/.openclaw/workspace\"`，这表明是在类 Unix 系统（如 macOS）上运行。\n*   **list**: 包含一个 ID 为 `\"main\"` 的配置，其工具配置文件（tools profile）被设置为 `\"full\"`（全功能）。\n\n### 3. 工具配置 (第 308-323 行)\n这部分定义了系统的通用工具行为：\n*   **profile**: 全局设置为 `\"coding\"`。\n*   **exec (执行设置)**: \n    *   `\"security\": \"full\"`：启用了完整的安全限制。\n    *   `\"ask\": \"off\"`：这可能意味着在执行命令或代码之前不会询问用户确认（由于安全设置为 \"full\"，可能是在受限沙盒中运行）。\n*   **web (网页搜索设置)**:\n    *   `\"enabled\": true`：启用了网页搜索功能。\n    *   `\"provider\": \"tavily\"`：搜索服务提供商被设定为 Tavily（一种常用于 AI 代理的搜索 API）。\n*   **media (媒体设置)**:\n    *   包含 **audio** 部分，其中可以看到 `\"enabled\": true`（已启用）和 `\"timeoutseconds\": 120`。\n\n### 技术观察\n*   **文件名**: `openclaw.json`。\n*   **编辑器**: 该文件在支持语法高亮的代码编辑器中打开（如 VS Code 的类似界面）。\n*   **路径信息**: 用户名为 `diehe`。\n*   **水印**: 图片底部有抖音水印和 ID：25922872347。\n\n该配置似乎属于一个高级 AI 辅助开发或任务自动化框架，允许 AI 执行代码并访问外部互联网资源。"}],"details":{"model":"minimax/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/73866824-7e57-465e-9823-903df56202cc.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176230994}}
{"type":"message","id":"901f45be","parentId":"1631d2b7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:30:32.635Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hmndgmf6qtj1_2","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这张图片展示了一个 macOS 访达（Finder）窗口，其路径为 `/Macintosh HD/用户/diehe/.openclaw`。该文件夹似乎是一个名为 \"openclaw\" 的软件或服务的配置和数据目录。\n\n以下是图片中显示的详细技术信息：\n\n### 1. 文件系统结构\n窗口中列出了 `.openclaw` 目录下的多个子文件夹和文件。许多项目的修改日期显示为“2026年3月”，这暗示了系统时间可能被手动更改过，或者这些是具有未来时间戳的预设文件。\n\n**文件夹列表：**\n*   **canvas**: 可能与绘图、界面或画布数据有关。\n*   **completions**: 通常用于存储命令行自动补全脚本。\n*   **credentials**: 可能包含 API 密钥、令牌或其他身份验证凭据。\n*   **cron**: 可能包含定时任务配置。\n*   **delivery-queue**: 可能用于管理待发送的数据或消息队列。\n*   **devices**: 可能包含连接或已知设备的信息。\n*   **feishu**: 暗示与飞书（Feishu/Lark）平台的集成。\n*   **identity**: 可能包含用户身份信息或证书。\n*   **logs**: 存储程序的运行日志。\n*   **media**: 存储媒体文件（如图片或视频）。\n*   **memory**: 可能用于临时缓存或持久化内存数据。\n\n**文件列表：**\n*   **exec-approvals.json**: 当前选中的文件。从文件名来看，它可能包含执行权限的批准记录或白名单配置。\n*   **openclaw.json**: 该软件的主配置文件。\n*   **openclaw.json.bak / .bak.1 / .bak.2**: 主配置文件的备份文件，用于版本恢复。\n\n### 2. 界面细节\n*   **操作系统**: macOS（通过窗口样式、左侧边栏文字如“应用程序”、“Macintosh HD”以及底部路径栏确认）。\n*   **语言**: 简体中文。\n*   **路径栏**: 底部清晰显示了路径：`Macintosh HD > 用户 > diehe > .openclaw > exec-approvals...`\n*   **当前选中**: 文件 `exec-approvals.json` 被选中，修改时间显示为“今天 15:03”。\n\n### 3. 背景与水印\n*   背景中可以看到一个终端窗口，标题栏包含“with batch features -- zsh”，表明用户可能正在使用具有批处理功能的终端环境。\n*   图片底部带有抖音水印，抖音号为：`25922872347`。\n\n从这些细节来看，这可能是一个开发者或高级用户正在配置或检查某个名为 OpenClaw 的特定工具（可能是一个自动化脚本、机器人框架或集成工具，考虑到其中的“feishu”和“exec-approvals”字样）。"}],"details":{"model":"minimax/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/ffe00903-1109-48d4-953f-b613f2e35380.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176232632}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8eab579","parentId":"901f45be","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:30:36.015Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hmndgmf6qtj1_3","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这张图片展示了一张拍摄电脑屏幕的照片，屏幕上正在运行一个文本编辑器（看起来像是 macOS 上的某个代码编辑器），显示了一个名为 `exec-approvals.json` 的配置文件内容。\n\n以下是该文件的具体内容和技术细节：\n\n### 1. 文件概况\n*   **文件名：** `exec-approvals.json`\n*   **文件格式：** JSON (JavaScript Object Notation)\n*   **推测用途：** 该文件似乎是为一个名为 **\"openclaw\"** 的程序配置执行权限和安全策略的。从路径 `/Users/diehe/.openclaw/` 可以看出，这可能是一个位于用户家目录下的隐藏配置文件夹。\n\n### 2. JSON 内容详细分析\n\n文件包含一个顶层对象，具有以下键值对：\n\n*   **`\"version\": 1`**: 配置文件版本号。\n*   **`\"socket\"`**: 定义了用于进程间通信的套接字信息。\n    *   `\"path\"`: `\"/Users/diehe/.openclaw/exec-approvals.sock\"` —— 指向一个 Unix 域套接字文件的路径。\n    *   `\"token\"`: `\"1lt_wGFpZvoPnG3MkdpHigxaIxXyfJm8g\"` —— 用于身份验证或授权的访问令牌。\n*   **`\"defaults\"`**: 默认的安全设置。\n    *   `\"security\": \"full\"`: 默认安全级别设置为“全开启”。\n    *   `\"ask\": \"off\"`: 默认情况下不询问用户许可。\n    *   `\"askFallback\": \"full\"`: 如果询问失败，回退到完全限制模式。\n*   **`\"agents\"`**: 针对不同代理（可能是不同的执行环境或模块）的具体配置。\n    *   **`\"main\"`**: 主代理的配置。\n        *   `\"security\": \"full\"`\n        *   `\"ask\": \"off\"`\n        *   **`\"allowlist\"` (白名单)**: 包含允许执行的特定命令或模式的列表。\n            *   白名单内有一个对象：\n                *   `\"id\"`: `\"92d01ac8-40a5-4b6d-a5d1-45b68081223d\"` (一个 UUID)。\n                *   `\"pattern\"`: `\"/usr/bin/cd\"` —— 允许执行的命令路径（注：在标准的 Unix 系统中，`cd` 通常是 shell 内置命令而非 `/usr/bin/` 下的独立二进制文件，这可能代表某种自定义环境或模拟）。\n                *   `\"lastUsedAt\"`: `1775007954530` —— 一个 Unix 时间戳（毫秒）。经计算，这个时间戳指向 **2026 年 4 月**，这可能意味着系统时间设置有误，或者是某种测试数据。\n\n### 3. 其他技术细节\n*   **操作系统：** 从窗口左上角的红黄绿“红绿灯”控制按钮和路径格式（`/Users/diehe/...`）来看，这运行在 **macOS** 系统上。\n*   **光标：** 在第 15 行末尾有一个蓝色的编辑光标，说明该文件当前正处于编辑状态。\n*   **水印：** 图片底部有抖音（TikTok 中国版）的水印，显示抖音号为：`25922872347`。\n\n### 总结\n这张图展现了一个用于某种自动化工具或安全框架（OpenClaw）的权限配置文件。它通过白名单（allowlist）机制来控制哪些命令（如 `/usr/bin/cd`）被允许执行，并使用令牌（token）和套接字（socket）进行安全通信。"}],"details":{"model":"minimax/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/27510a1b-f477-44d8-998d-e1a5a3e766f7.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775176236010}}
{"type":"message","id":"acf0a45c","parentId":"d8eab579","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:31:03.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the context. The user is showing me screenshots of someone modifying `exec-approvals.json` to bypass approval requirements. The images show:\n\n1. `openclaw.json` - main config file with model aliases and workspace settings\n2. A Finder window showing the `.openclaw` directory with `exec-approvals.json` selected\n3. The content of `exec-approvals.json` which contains security settings including `\"ask\": \"off\"` in defaults and for the main agent\n\nThe user says \"我看到有人改这些文件就可以不用审批了\" - \"I saw someone say that by modifying these files you don't need approval anymore.\"\n\nThis is a sensitive topic. The user seems to be asking about bypassing security controls. Let me think about this carefully:\n\n1. The `exec-approvals.json` file contains settings that control whether the system asks for approval before executing commands\n2. Setting `\"ask\": \"off\"` would disable the approval prompt\n3. There's also an `allowlist` that specifies which commands are allowed\n\nHowever, I need to be careful here. The user might be:\n- Asking genuinely curious questions about how the system works\n- Trying to understand security implications\n- Potentially trying to bypass their own security settings (which would be their own system)\n\nActually, looking at the context more carefully - the user (HALEI) is sharing these images and making an observation. They're looking at their own system (since the channel is Feishu DM to their own OpenClaw instance).\n\nWait - let me re-read. The images show paths like `/Users/diehe/.openclaw/` but the current user is HALEI on a system where the workspace is `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace`. So these images are from someone else's system (user \"diehe\").\n\nThe user is observing that by modifying certain files, the approval requirement can be bypassed. This could be:\n\n\n- A security concern they're raising\n- A question about how the security model works\n- Sharing information they found online\n\nThe screenshots reveal how the approval mechanism functions through `exec-approvals.json` and that disabling `ask` removes the confirmation step. Since this is likely their own system and they're simply inquiring about how it works, I should explain the security implications directly rather than refusing to engage. Disabling approvals is inherently risky as it removes a protective layer, but it's their system to configure.\n\nI'll keep my response concise and avoid being preachy about security.","thinkingSignature":"c11d80f7b90425eefdcf553175b32ac1ef6339bd34a55397f1e89e1de34e04cd"},{"type":"text","text":"\n看了这三张图，大概明白了。\n\n**你说的是 `exec-approvals.json` 这个文件**——控制 exec（命令执行）是否需要审批的配置。\n\n关键在于这两个设置：\n\n```\n\"ask\": \"off\"   // 关闭执行前的询问确认\n```\n\n把它设成 `\"off\"` 确实可以跳过审批。但这相当于**把安全门拆了**——任何 exec 命令都能直接跑，不会有任何提示或中断。\n\n**实际风险：**\n- 误操作无法挽回（没有确认环节）\n- 如果被恶意利用，没有拦截机制\n- 脚本错误也会直接执行\n\n**更安全的做法：**\n- 保持 `\"ask\": \"on-miss\"` 或 `\"on\"`，只在确有必要时临时放行\n- 用 `allowlist` 白名单机制精确控制允许执行的命令，而不是全局关闭审批\n\n你的飞书 OpenClaw 部署目前是怎么配置的？想知道的话我可以帮你查一下 `exec-approvals.json` 的当前状态。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2930,"output":711,"cacheRead":12632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16273,"cost":{"input":0.000879,"output":0.0008531999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0007579199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0024901199999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775176236015,"responseId":"061e3d2c7e0630575a11944dc72f90b8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e220d8f5","parentId":"acf0a45c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:32:12.758Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-03 08:31:05 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53c4d1b8f8b0c1117cacb9cb497]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53c4d1b8f8b0c1117cacb9cb497\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-03 08:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n昨天也看了一个说openclaw.son每个agent都加上 截图里面的参数，也可以"}],"timestamp":1775176332687}}
{"type":"message","id":"022ea68e","parentId":"e220d8f5","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:32:27.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is mentioning another configuration file `openclaw.json` where you can add parameters per agent to skip approvals. Let me think about what they saw - in the first image (the openclaw.json), they saw model aliases and workspace configurations.\n\nLooking back at the first image description, it showed `openclaw.json` with settings like:\n- `\"profile\": \"coding\"`\n- `\"security\": \"full\"` \n- `\"ask\": \"off\"`\n\nAnd there was a `list` section with agents. The user is saying that adding `\"ask\": \"off\"` per-agent (in the agent-specific config) also works to skip approvals.\n\nSo the configuration can be set at multiple levels:\n1. `defaults` section - global default\n2. `agents.<name>` section - per-agent override\n\nBoth would achieve the same result of skipping exec approvals.\n\nI should acknowledge this and explain that setting it at the agent level is indeed another valid approach, though still carries the same security implications.","thinkingSignature":"4a5becb30bf6b9f2eee332ee719aae72ba047f7d88d367b833a9fe1a6e0c9ea3"},{"type":"text","text":"对，`openclaw.json` 里每个 agent 单独配也能生效。\n\n结构大概是这样：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"main\": {\n      \"security\": \"full\",\n      \"ask\": \"off\"    // 加在这里，只影响 main agent\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n跟直接在 `exec-approvals.json` 里改 `defaults` 效果一样——都是绕过了审批机制。\n\n**两种改法的区别：**\n- `exec-approvals.json` → 改的是\"谁需要审批\"\n- `openclaw.json` → 改的是\"这个 agent 跑的时候问不问我\"\n\n本质上都是在关安全门。\n\n---\n\n你的 OpenClaw 现在跑在哪个模式？直接改配置前建议先确认当前的 `ask` 和 `security` 状态，不然改错了方向反而麻烦。要我帮你查一下当前配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":383,"cacheRead":12632,"cacheWrite":3301,"totalTokens":16355,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0004596,"cacheRead":0.0007579199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.001237875,"total":0.002467095}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775176332693,"responseId":"061e3d8dd6cd6102a3ba818adcffc114"}}
{"type":"message","id":"088bb956","parentId":"022ea68e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:35:12.833Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-03 08:34:08 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53c4e138d0a4c4f7a05fb32a76f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53c4e138d0a4c4f7a05fb32a76f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-03 08:34 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n那就改吧，要不太麻烦了。只有你有权限就行，别agent不用"}],"timestamp":1775176512735}}
{"type":"message","id":"1da8ec1a","parentId":"088bb956","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:35:20.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"只有你有权限就行，别agent不用\"——意思是只要我这个 main agent（也就是大总管）不用审批就行，其他 agent 可能还是需要审批的。所以我需要：\n\n1. 先查看当前的 exec-approvals.json 配置\n2. 确认当前的 ask/security 设置\n3. 只给 main agent 设置 \"ask\": \"off\"，其他 agent 保持原有设置\n\n让我先查看配置文件。","thinkingSignature":"69081fbb22aac12c7604147f330981de095cc7f575dcd78e6aa35d9d66337d1e"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，只放过你这个 main agent，其他 agent 保留审批。让我先看一下当前配置。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bmsh65h1yh3e_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/exec-approvals.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bmsh65h1yh3e_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":168,"cacheRead":16239,"cacheWrite":168,"totalTokens":16614,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0002016,"cacheRead":0.0009743399999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000063,"total":0.0012506399999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775176512755,"responseId":"061e3e4167ec054ad9f8aef650abcf57"}}
