{"type":"message","id":"72b3d844","parentId":"06a4e647","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:36:12.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"修改成功了。现在配置变成了：\n\n```json\n\"defaults\": {\n  \"ask\": \"off\"\n},\n\"agents\": {\n  \"main\": {\n    \"allowlist\": [...]\n  },\n  \"tts\": {\n    \"ask\": \"on\",  // 新增的，保持审批\n    \"allowlist\": [...]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n这样：\n- main agent：默认不用审批（因为 defaults.ask = \"off\"）\n- tts agent：需要审批（因为明确设置了 ask: \"on\"）\n\n等等，我需要再想一下逻辑对不对...\n\n实际上看 OpenClaw 的 exec 审批逻辑：\n- 如果 agent 有明确的 ask 设置，用那个\n- 否则用 defaults 的\n\n所以：\n- main：没有明确 ask，用 defaults → \"off\" → 不用审批 ✓\n- tts：明确 ask: \"on\" → 需要审批 ✓\n\n这是对的。让我告诉用户修改完成。","thinkingSignature":"001dd34c101c86b7396cb3c73f7210a8814c5a86e437b787ac8f2b6caf50fee2"},{"type":"text","text":"改好了。新的配置逻辑：\n\n- **`defaults.ask = \"off\"`** — 所有 agent 默认免审批\n- **`agents.tts.ask = \"on\"`** — 单独给 tts（选品大师）保留审批\n\nmain 你这个 agent 不需要任何变更，直接就不弹审批了。tts 还是老样子。\n\n生效不需要重启，改完立即可用。可以试一条 exec 命令验证一下。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9494,"output":275,"cacheRead":12632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22401,"cost":{"input":0.0028482,"output":0.00033,"cacheRead":0.0007579199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0039361199999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775176562786,"responseId":"061e3e733b62714346130b3c506f1ad4"}}
