{"type":"message","id":"f8c206a1","parentId":"73a27c59","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:48:48.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to look at a cloud document (飞书云文档) that contains the product selector agent design plan. They mentioned I used this design yesterday, and the agent has been set up but only initially. Let me fetch the Feishu docs to find this document.","thinkingSignature":"a75c54d20e15368c4088da9b50a5d4e6b48320c50dff04da1e9e9bf50c06aeb2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d52uvo92jp8o_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-fetch-doc/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39,"output":108,"cacheRead":12632,"cacheWrite":19826,"totalTokens":32605,"cost":{"input":0.0000117,"output":0.0001296,"cacheRead":0.0007579199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00743475,"total":0.00833397}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775177322698,"responseId":"061e416bf65feb64faf2bcf5b6518ed5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2222fd28","parentId":"f8c206a1","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:48:48.188Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d52uvo92jp8o_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-fetch-doc\ndescription: |\n  获取飞书云文档内容。返回文档的 Markdown 内容，支持处理文档中的图片、文件和画板（需配合 feishu_doc_media 工具）。\n---\n\n# feishu_mcp_fetch_doc\n\n获取飞书云文档的 Markdown 内容（Lark-flavored 格式）。\n\n## 重要：图片、文件、画板的处理\n\n**文档中的图片、文件、画板需要通过 `feishu_doc_media`（action: download）工具单独获取！**\n\n### 识别格式\n\n返回的 Markdown 中，媒体文件以 HTML 标签形式出现：\n\n- **图片**：\n  ```html\n  <image token=\"Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc\" width=\"1833\" height=\"2491\" align=\"center\"/>\n  ```\n\n- **文件**：\n  ```html\n  <view type=\"1\">\n    <file token=\"Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc\" name=\"skills.zip\"/>\n  </view>\n  ```\n\n- **画板**：\n  ```html\n  <whiteboard token=\"Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc\"/>\n  ```\n\n### 获取步骤\n\n1. 从 HTML 标签中提取 `token` 属性值\n2. 调用 `feishu_doc_media` 下载：\n   ```json\n   {\n     \"action\": \"download\",\n     \"resource_token\": \"提取的token\",\n     \"resource_type\": \"media\",\n     \"output_path\": \"/path/to/save/file\"\n   }\n   ```\n\n## 参数\n\n- **`doc_id`**（必填）：支持直接传文档 URL 或 token\n  - 直接传 URL：`https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc`（系统自动提取 token）\n  - 直接传 token：`Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc`\n  - 知识库 URL/token 也支持：`https://xxx.feishu.cn/wiki/Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc` 或 `Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc`\n\n## Wiki URL 处理策略\n\n知识库链接（`/wiki/TOKEN`）背后可能是云文档、电子表格、多维表格等不同类型的文档。当不确定类型时, **不能直接假设是云文档**，必须先查询实际类型。\n\n### 处理流程\n\n1. **先调用 `feishu_wiki_space_node`（action: get）解析 wiki token**：\n   ```json\n   { \"action\": \"get\", \"token\": \"wiki_token_here\" }\n   ```\n2. **从返回的 `node` 中获取 `obj_type`（实际文档类型）和 `obj_token`（实际文档 token）**\n3. **根据 `obj_type` 调用对应工具**：\n\n| obj_type | 工具 | 传参 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| `docx` | `feishu_mcp_fetch_doc` | doc_id = obj_token |\n| `sheet` | `feishu_sheet` | spreadsheet_token = obj_token |\n| `bitable` | `feishu_bitable_*` 系列 | app_token = obj_token |\n| 其他 | 告知用户暂不支持该类型 | — |\n\n\n### 示例\n\n用户：`帮我看下这个文档 https://xxx.feishu.cn/wiki/ABC123`\n\n1. 调用 `feishu_wiki_space_node`（action: get, token: ABC123）\n2. 返回 `obj_type: \"docx\"`, `obj_token: \"doxcnXYZ789\"`\n3. 调用 `feishu_mcp_fetch_doc`（doc_id: doxcnXYZ789）\n\n## 工具组合\n\n| 需求 | 工具 |\n|------|------|\n| 获取文档文本 | `feishu_mcp_fetch_doc` |\n| 下载图片/文件/画板 | `feishu_doc_media`（action: download） |\n| 解析 wiki token 类型 | `feishu_wiki_space_node`（action: get） |\n| 读写电子表格 | `feishu_sheet` |\n| 操作多维表格 | `feishu_bitable_*` 系列 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775177328183}}
{"type":"message","id":"71fc916c","parentId":"2222fd28","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:48:55.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to find the Feishu document about the product selector agent design. But I don't have a direct doc ID. Let me search for it. I can use the feishu search functionality or look through recently accessed documents. Actually, I should try to search for the document. Let me check if there's a way to search docs in Feishu.\n\nActually, looking at the feishu skill, I can try to use the feishu search. But I don't see a search_doc skill listed. Let me try to use the feishu fetch doc with the document URL if the user shared it, or I can try to look in the workspace for any references to the doc.\n\n\nThe user mentioned there's a cloud document with the design plan, but didn't share the link. I could try searching through recently accessed documents or check if there's a doc ID stored in the workspace. Let me look for the feishu search skill to find it.","thinkingSignature":"46dfb11d1ea60e451002e8b96ac9964fc8c6c518e79f22369b9331452f3638cc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g7efinije4la_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20845,"output":232,"cacheRead":12632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33709,"cost":{"input":0.0062534999999999995,"output":0.0002784,"cacheRead":0.0007579199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007289819999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775177328188,"responseId":"061e4170c3b771491d049dcc2a16952c"}}
