{"type":"message","id":"661053e8","parentId":"3f0e9d4b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:49:03.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I don't see a Feishu search skill. But the feishu plugin should have feishu search. Let me try to use `sessions_spawn` with feishu tool or use the feishu search capability. Actually, I should try using the feishu_im tools to search for messages mentioning the doc.\n\nWait, let me think differently. The user says \"查看云文档，里面有一个 选品agent设计方案\" - they're telling me to check the cloud document. Maybe I should ask them for the document URL/link, or maybe there's a way to list recent documents.\n\nActually, looking at the feishu plugin tools, there's `feishu_search_doc_wiki` which might help. \n\nLet me try that. Or maybe the user already shared the doc in a previous message - let me check the session history to see if there's a link.","thinkingSignature":"d232cfe88a28631e4e861d9b544ef1b2d1517b8dbfb72384ac6f7e69a8dc8762"},{"type":"text","text":"没有文档链接，我搜一下最近的会话看有没有提过：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lhhfmyaaxjxt_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb","limit":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":21125,"output":254,"cacheRead":12632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34011,"cost":{"input":0.006337499999999999,"output":0.0003048,"cacheRead":0.0007579199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007400219999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775177336007,"responseId":"061e4178620a226bf415534097c39443"}}
{"type":"message","id":"745b6fa5","parentId":"661053e8","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:49:03.678Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lhhfmyaaxjxt_1","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The update-check shows version 2026.3.22 is available, but we have 2026.4.1 installed based on what I saw in the openclaw.json `\\\"lastTouchedVersion\\\": \\\"2026.4.1\\\"`. So the upgrade to 4.1 was done manually.\\n\\nLet me check the memory system. I need to verify:\\n1. The LanceDB database (lcm.db) - check if it's working\\n2. The memory-lancedb plugin status\\n\\nFrom openclaw.json:\\n- `\\\"memory\\\": \\\"memory-lancedb\\\"` in plugins.slots\\n- memory-lancedb is enabled with config that includes an embedding API key\\n\\nLet me try to verify the memory system is working by checking if I can interact with it.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_u7i3mmnpw7fk_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/lcm.db* 2>/dev/null\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775177147361,\n      \"responseId\": \"061e40bb7625b288a0ec6519c1e38a6a\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"f073030d\",\n        \"seq\": 72\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Hmm, the `ls -la` fails but `ls` without `-la` works. The issue might be with the `-la` flag containing a path or something. Let me just try `l