minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775177161600,\n      \"responseId\": \"061e40ca9b55e672a50ae8fdd4ca875f\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"8ebbed56\",\n        \"seq\": 78\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"There's a `main.sqlite` and `lancedb-pro` directory. Let me check the lancedb-pro directory to see if it's the memory-lancedb data.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_f7j9bvz8cnru_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"ls /home/halei/.openclaw/memory/lancedb-pro/\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775177163950,\n      \"responseId\": \"061e40cc987e48b3bafb07d08b26284b\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"5da0b964\",\n        \"seq\": 80\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Good, the LanceDB memories file exists. Let me also check the backups directory.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_function_6noh0twq137i_1\",\n          \"name\": \"exec\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"command\": \"ls /home/halei/.openclaw/memory/backups/\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775177167230,\n      \"responseId\": \"061e40cf4e5a9623b71ab13805486790\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"f0249b45\",\n        \"seq\": 82\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"Empty backups directory. Let me now summarize what I found:\\n\\n1. **OpenClaw version**: 4.1 (from openclaw.json `lastTouchedVersion: \\\"2026.4.1\\\"`)\\n2. **Memory plugin**: `memory-lancedb` is enabled and configured with embedding API key\\n3. **Database files**:\\n   - `/home/halei/.openclaw/lcm.db` exists\\n   - `/home/halei/.openclaw/memory/lancedb-pro/memories.lance` exists\\n   - `/home/halei/.openclaw/memory/main.sqlite` exists\\n4. **No MEMORY.md file** - this is missing, which means the curated long-term memory hasn't been created\\n5. **Daily memory files** exist from 03-25, 03-27, 04-01, 04-02\\n\\nThe memory system seems to be in place - LanceDB is configured and the data files exist. But there's no MEMORY.md which according to AGENTS.md should contain long-term curated memories.\\n\\n\\nI should verify whether the embedding API key is actually valid and check if LanceDB is functioning as expected. I could run the openclaw doctor command to get a more comprehensive system status, though I might need to try a different approach since standard commands could have allowlist issues.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"\\n看了下系统状态：\\n\\n**版本 & 插件**\\n- OpenClaw 4.1 ✅ 已安装运行\\n- `memory-lancedb` ✅ 已启用，embedding 配置正常\\n\\n**数据库文件**\\n- `lcm.db` ✅ 存在\\n- `memory/lancedb-pro/memories.lance` ✅ 存在\\n- `memory/main.sqlite` ✅ 存在\\n\\n**记忆文件**\\n- 日志文件只有 03-25、03-27、04-01、04-02 的记录\\n- `MEMORY.md`（长期记忆）不存在 — 这个是空的\\n\\n**一个小问题**：`memory/backups/` 是空的，不知道升级时有没有自动备份。\\n\\n要我跑一下 `openclaw doctor` 做完整诊断吗？或者你想先看看选品agent的优化需求是什么？\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1775177170707,\n      \"responseId\": \"061e40d30039ebad9fbf10c0244e41ef\",\n      \"__openclaw