分150-199，月销≥200单\",\n    \"   - B级：评分100-149，月销≥100单\",\n    \"   - C级：评分<100，月销<100单\",\n    \"\",\n    \"### 输出规范\",\n    \"1. 飞书表格字段固定：\",\n    \"   - 1688链接（确认链接部分）\",\n    \"   - 标准化时间格式（2026年4月）\",\n    \"\",\n    \"2. 人工审核流程：\",\n    \"   10:00自动通知\",\n    \"   异常时将推送至Slack\",\n    \"\",\n    \"## 系统提示词（Agent Directive）\",\n    \"```system_reminder markdown\"\n    \"• 主要状态定位：主动参与私信对话\",\n    \"• 输出格式：\",\n    \"  1. 输出完成：发送信息过滤标记「🟢发送完成」\",\n    \"  2. 进度中：提示「⏳数据处理中」\",\n    \"• 错误处理：\",\n    \"  - API失败→重试3次后进入休眠状态5分钟\",\n    \"  - 表格创建失败→触发故障排查流程\",\n    \"```\n    \"• 完成指令：发送信息标记「✅ 任务完成」\"\n  \"```\",\n    \"\",\n    \"## 巅权配色说明\",\n    \"• 系统指示色：\",\n    \"  - 蓝色：系统核心引导符号\",\n    \"  - 红色：风险等级标志\",\n    \"• 提示视图：\",\n    \"  - ⭐：评分指示灯\",\n    \"  - 🔒：IP合规标志\",\n    \"• 状态指示符：\",\n    \"  - ⏳：数据处理中\",\n    \"  - ✅：操作完成\",\n    \"  - ⚠️：风险警示\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请用户确认是否需要调整任何细节。完整文件将被写入`/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/TTS-选品专家-SOUL.md`，建议事后验证文件内容。\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/free","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775117329853,"responseId":"gen-1775117330-6BdM9GY6kMmUyeUwnspe","__openclaw":{"id":"4073a3c3","seq":64}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"An async command did not run.\nDo not run the command again.\nThere is no new command output.\nDo not mention, summarize, or reuse output from any earlier run in this session.\n\nExact completion details:\nExec denied (gateway id=2aa6d0fc-2390-4e15-a86d-2975b56d0f88, approval-timeout): grep -r -i \"tts\\|hair\\|scout\\|选品\" /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/feishu-multi-agent-manager/ || echo \"No matches found\"\n\nReply to the user in a helpful way.\nExplain that the command did not run and why.\nDo not claim there is new command output."}],"timestamp":1775119185141,"__openclaw":{"id":"67ecbeb4","seq":65}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","stopReason":"error","timestamp":