nt_style\":{\"bold\":false,\"inline_code\":false,\"italic\":false,\"strikethrough\":false,\"underline\":false}}}],\"style\":{\"align\":1,\"folded\":false}}},{\"block_id\":\"doxcnGaSdFnQssPPKfW902yUosd\",\"block_type\":32,\"children\":[\"doxcnKMBuR9czoDSKsx5mNgxvch\"],\"parent_id\":\"doxcnqMpBMZjrMsNgTae88VzNCe\",\"table_cell\":{}},{\"block_id\":\"doxcnKMBuR9czoDSKsx5mNgxvch\",\"block_type\":2,\"parent_id\":\"doxcnGaSdFnQssPPKfW902yUosd\",\"text\":{\"elements\":[{\"text_run\":{\"content\":\"9:00-9:45\",\"text_element_style\":{\"bold\":false,\"inline_code\":false,\"italic\":false,\"strikethrough\":false,\"underline\":false}}}],\"style\":{\"align\":1,\"folded\":false}}},{\"block_id\":\"doxcnf51RmeRpMdRuGr37mvMRbd\",\"block_type\":32,\"children\":[\"doxcns3Hfiipi0vqePjXbqQlbGd\"],\"parent_id\":\"doxcnqMpBMZjrMsNgTae88VzNCe\",\"table_cell\":{}}],\"page_token\":\"wrorAcOIw6jDq2AXwqPDnhLDhX1fe8KVLcKoe8K8UgrDqWZPwpQFZ1bDmMKewprDsFTCocOxBsK3w7jDv1rCvcK0TEc7wojDhMKwwo7Cn1NYLMOKTSrDijfDi2HDo20gw6jDlG3Dm8KRwqDDpFrCiyAXw4_DkcO1EX7Dsx_DusK1ESZpw5jCiUILe8KrHzYywqdIw5vDgcKDXnl6EMKLcB8Zw6_DklbCg3HChXzCicOEwrEDHSvDk24HOk_Ds8K5Vnc9GWDCvE9OIXbDg8K7d2ll\"},\"msg\":\"success\"}","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775177812755}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb0cfffe","parentId":"9a6193c0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:57:39.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I got the document content. Let me parse this more carefully. The document is \"TikTok 东南亚发饰选品策略（泰越站点）v2.0\" dated 2026-04-02. \n\nFrom the content I can see:\n\n1. **核心定位**: \"数据驱动的东南亚发饰选品专家\" - focusing on Thailand and Vietnam TikTok Shop hair accessories category\n\n2. **双轨并行策略**:\n   - 轨道1: 主动选品（日常款）- based on TikTok后台 + InfluTalk data\n   - 轨道2: 跟品策略（爆款跟随）- based on EchoTik热销榜 + 妙手采集\n   \n3. **市场特征对比**: Each market has distinct pricing preferences, material inclinations, and logistics tolerances that shape their purchasing behavior.\n\n4. **数据来源与工具**: TikTok Shop后台 provides free daily insights, InfluTalk offers detailed sales metrics for a fee, and EchoTik tracks livestreaming and video content performance.\n\nAdditional platforms include 1688 for real-time procurement data at no cost, Google Trends for weekly seasonal analysis, WebSurf for browser automation that's already integrated, and 妙手 for one-click 1688 product sourcing that's also deployed.\n\nThe system is connected to 飞书多维表格 for collaborative data management and 飞书文档 for report generation and knowledge storage, both configured and ready.\n\nThe workflow unfolds across five stages: data collection and initial screening at 9:00 AM, followed by deep analysis and profit calculations, then recommendation grading, execution with coordination, and finally tracking with iteration.\n\nThe screening criteria eliminate any listings with intellectual property risks, sensitive content, platform violations, or non-compliant materials, while requiring at least 100 orders in the past month, proper categorization, and target market validation.\n\nAdditional requirements include weight under 200g, ratings of 4.5 or higher, and return rates below 5% to ensure product quality and customer satisfaction.\n\nFor Vietnam specifically, pricing strategy multiplies the sum of procurement and shipping costs by 3500 then 1.2, targeting a minimum 20% gross margin, whereas Thailand applies a 5.0 multiplier and 1.25 factor for a 25% margin threshold.\n\nSupplier selection prioritizes stores with ratings of 4.5 or above, 48-hour or faster delivery, and at least 20% repeat purchase rate, with most orders having a maximum quantity of 100 units for the first shipment. Recommended industrial clusters include Yiwu for variety, Guangzhou for quality, and Shantou for acrylic products.\n\nThe recommendation grading system sorts products into S, A, B, and C tiers based on monthly order volume—S grade requires 500 or more orders, A grade requires 200-499 orders, and B grade starts at 100 orders.\n\nAdditional grading factors include gross margin thresholds (30%+ for S, 25%+ for A, 20-24% for B), weight limits (100g or less for S, 150g or less for A, 200g or less for B), and supplier ratings (4.8+ for S, 4.5+ for A, 4.0+ for B). S grade items are recommended for immediate procurement of 50-100 units initially, A grade for normal procurement of 30-50 units, and B grade enters an observation pool awaiting growth signals. C grade products are automatically excluded. Bonus points are awarded for growth rates exceeding 30% and other positive indicators.\n\nThe final workflow connects the selection agent to human reviewers for a 10-30 minute daily review, then branches to specialized agents handling content, operations, customer service, and supply chain. Launch strategy differentiates between broad testing with 50-100 items at 10-30 units each for 1-2 week observation periods versus focused development of 5-10 potential items at 50-200 units over 1-3 month cycles. Tracking happens daily for sales and competitor changes, weekly for identifying top performers and laggards, and monthly for analyzing success and failure patterns.\n\nThe output includes a comprehensive multi-dimensional table tracking product name, TikTok title, site, three-level category, local currency price, monthly sales volume, 30-day volume, growth rate, 1688 comparison links, recommended procurement sources, cost prices in CNY, estimated profit, profit margin, IP risk level (none/low/medium/high), recommendation grade (S/A/B/C), action recommendations (immediate procurement/observe/abandon), and collection status. Multiple views support filtering by all products, S-grade only, high-margin items above 50%, high-growth items above 30%, or pending review items. The reporting template follows a structured format for the hair accessories selection report.\n\nThe document also establishes strict IP infringement boundaries excluding major brands like Disney, Sanrio, Line Friends, anime properties, and luxury brands, along with material compliance requirements specific to Thailand (nickel release limits and toy safety standards) and Vietnam (heavy metal restrictions and ROHS certification for plastics). Platform violations covering counterfeit goods, IP infringement, and dangerous materials are clearly defined as grounds for store closure or removal.\n\nFor execution, I'm mapping out a 30-minute daily workflow starting at 9:00 with automated product scanning and grading, followed by human review of results between 10-11am, then supply chain verification of recommended suppliers and logistics tracking for new product samples. The tts agent has been established but only at a basic level based on session logs from the past day.\n\nThe earlier sub-agent attempted to optimize the system prompt but ran into execution approval timeouts and depleted OpenRouter credits, so it never completed writing the new prompt to file. To move forward, I need to review what actually got stored in the workspace, understand what remains unimplemented from the design spec, and then create a concrete optimization plan starting with proper system prompt configuration.","thinkingSignature":"09f566801765517c67e97bf5ee3766946653796de8f2cb73582b20d0f6a9f23c"},{"type":"text","text":"文档读到了。方案 v2.0，2026-04-02 更新的。内容非常详细。\n\n**文档核心结构：**\n\n- **双轨选品**：主动选品（日常）+ 跟品策略（爆款）\n- **5阶段流程**：数据采集 → 深度分析 → 等级判定 → 执行联动 → 跟踪迭代\n- **利润公式**：越南 `(采购价+头程)×3500×1.2`，泰国 `(采购价+头程)×5.0×1.25`\n- **推荐等级**：S/A/B/C 级，有严格的销量、毛利、重量、评分门槛\n- **输出**：飞书多维表格（发饰选品表）+ 选品报告\n- **自动化工具**：WebSurf、妙手采集、飞书多维表格、飞书文档均已部署\n\n**当前状态（从会话记录看到的）：**\n\ntts agent 之前有人尝试优化过系统提示词，但：\n1. 审批超时导致 exec 命令多次失败\n2. 最后还碰到 OpenRouter 积分不足\n3. 优化后的内容没有实际写入文件\n\n所以现在的问题不是\"优化完了\"而是**根本没有落地**。\n\n下一步要把这个方案真正注入到 tts agent，需要：\n1. 确认当前 tts agent 的 SOUL.md / AGENTS.md 内容是什么状态\n2. 制定具体要改哪些文件（SOUL.md、还是新建配置文件）\n3. 逐步执行\n\n要我先看一下 tts agent 现在的配置文件状态吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98607,"output":1525,"cacheRead":12567,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112699,"cost":{"input":0.0295821,"output":0.0018299999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0007540199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03216612}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775177812768,"responseId":"061e4355454cba765a8f4ae12ad7bf4b"}}
